Harmony Gold’s Unisel Resumes Operations After July 7 Death of Mineworker

-- B y   M k h u l u l i   M a n c o t y w a
-- 
2011-07-12T07:17:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/harmony-gold-s-unisel-resumes-operations-after-july-7-death-of-mineworker.html
Harmony Gold Mining Co.’s Unisel
mine in  South Africa  resumed operations yesterday after being
shut since a worker died in a locomotive accident on July 7,
spokeswoman Henrika Basterfield said by phone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mkhululi Mancotywa in Johannesburg at 
